args = copy.deepcopy(base_args)

assert_raises(CCLError, ccllib.cl_tracer_t_new_wrapper, COSMO, 0, 0, *args)
assert_raises(CCLError, ccllib.angular_cl_vec, COSMO, None, None, None, 1, 
    0, pyccl.pyutils.integ_types['spline'], 'none', status)
